<subSubSection lastPageId="347" lastPageNumber="348" pageId="346" pageNumber="347" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="346.[151,1437,1782,2023]" lastBlockId="347.[151,1437,151,392]" lastPageId="347" lastPageNumber="348" pageId="346" pageNumber="347">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,455,1783,1806]" pageId="346" pageNumber="347">
Remarks. 
<emphasis box="[328,762,1782,1807]" italics="true" pageId="346" pageNumber="347">
Taxonomy. 
<taxonomicName box="[467,762,1782,1807]" class="Gastropoda" family="Drilliidae" genus="Syntomodrillia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="346" pageNumber="347" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="triangulos">Syntomodrillia triangulos</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</emphasis>
possesses the characteristics of the genus: small size, a fusiform shell sculpted with ribs extending from suture-to-suture and to the anterior fasciole on the last whorl, and a varix about ⅓-whorl from the edge of the outer lip. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[759,886,1854,1879]" italics="true" pageId="346" pageNumber="347">Variability.</emphasis>
Eight specimens have an average total length of 
<quantity box="[151,252,1891,1915]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.81" pageId="346" pageNumber="347" unit="mm" value="6.81">6.81 mm</quantity>
(
<quantity box="[267,407,1890,1915]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.95" metricValueMax="7.7" metricValueMin="6.2" pageId="346" pageNumber="347" unit="mm" value="6.95" valueMax="7.7" valueMin="6.2">6.2–7.7 mm</quantity>
), and an average W/ 
<taxonomicName box="[640,716,1890,1915]" class="Gastropoda" family="Drilliidae" genus="Lissodrillia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="346" pageNumber="347" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="ratio">L ratio</taxonomicName>
of 
<number box="[755,822,1891,1915]" pageId="346" pageNumber="347" value="0.395">0.395</number>
. 
<emphasis box="[833,1294,1890,1915]" italics="true" pageId="346" pageNumber="347">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[833,997,1890,1915]" italics="true" pageId="346" pageNumber="347">Identification.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[1004,1294,1890,1915]" class="Gastropoda" family="Drilliidae" genus="Syntomodrillia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="346" pageNumber="347" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="triangulos">Syntomodrillia triangulos</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
